Package project.models.feedback

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    I_Feedback
    Defines the functions for an object that is used for feedback.
    I_FeedbackRecipient
    Defines the functions of an object that receives feedback.
    I_FeedbackSender
    Annotates a class as being able to provide feedback.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Feedback
    Generic feedback class.
    FeedbackFactory
    A class that creates I_Feedback objects.
    FeedbackWithRating
    Feedback subclass that includes a rating.
